OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773349952
OL,3,CCornwall D-Day Veteran dies aged 101
OL,5,FA Cromwell tank driver from Callington
OL,6,Fwho was attached to the 7th Armoured
OL,7,FDivision has died at the age of 101.
OL,9,FRichard Aldred was driving a Cromwell
OL,10,Ftank at the age of 19. He arrived in
OL,11,FNormandy in July 1944.
OL,13,FFollowing his passing, the Veterans'
OL,14,FFoundation charity said: "We were sad
OL,15,Fto hear that Normandy Veteran Richard
OL,16,FAldred has passed away at the weekend
OL,17,Faged 101. His service will never be
OL,18,Fforgotten. Our thoughts are with his
OL,19,Ffamily and friends."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
