CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773349952
OL,3,CCornwall D-Day Veteran dies aged 101
OL,5,F"Richard visited the Memorial many
OL,6,Ftimes since its opening thanks to
OL,7,Fsupport from The Spirit of Normandy
OL,8,FTrust. In the 80th anniversary year of
OL,9,FD-Day, Richard became an Honorary
OL,10,FCitizen of Bourneville-Sainte-Croix.
OL,11,FRest in peace, Richard."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
